    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. This specimen features the S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the VANOS unit has been fully overhauled, rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, and the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Every factory VIN tag is present, and the suspension remains taut, preserving the original chassis dynamics. A zero-compromise example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
